---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
import PageHero from '../components/PageHero.astro'
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Tree Removal — Alderleaf"
  description="Professional tree removal on Haida Gwaii — safe take-down in limited spaces. Over 25 years in the industry."
  activePage="removal"
  heroImage="/images/Land-Clearing.jpg"
>
  <PageHero image="/images/Land-Clearing.jpg" imageClass="object-left-bottom">
    <p class="hero-eyebrow">Over 25 Years in the industry</p>
    <h1 class="hero-heading mt-3">Tree Removal</h1>
    <p class="hero-lead">From impeding viewscapes to presenting a danger to existing structures, there are many reasons why it may become necessary to completely remove a tree before the end of its lifespan. We have professional experience in a wide-range of tree removal scenarios, with a proven record of safety.</p>
    <a href="/quote" class="btn-hero-primary mt-8">Request a Free Quote</a>
  </PageHero>

  <section class="py-16 lg:py-24">
    <div class="site-container grid items-center gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-16">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-normal">Tree Removal</h2>
        <div class="section-divider mt-5"></div>
        <p class="mt-6 leading-relaxed">We specialize in the take-down, removal and cleanup of trees when there is limited space and danger to structures or other landscaping. We are equipped with specialized, heavy rigging which allows us to safely cut up and lower limbs and stem pieces in a controlled manner with consideration and protection for your property below. Fully insured and committed to safety, you can enjoy peace-of-mind when Alderleaf is on the job for your tree removal.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3">
        <img src="/images/IMG_5866.jpg" alt="Tree removal work" class="rounded-xl object-cover shadow-md" loading="lazy" />
        <img src="/images/IMG_5803.jpg" alt="Tree removal on Haida Gwaii" class="rounded-xl object-cover shadow-md" loading="lazy" />
        <img src="/images/20220630_114805.jpg" alt="Alderleaf crew at work" class="col-span-2 rounded-xl object-cover shadow-md" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-cream py-16 lg:py-24">
    <div class="site-container grid items-center gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-16">
      <img src="/images/IMG_1966.jpg" alt="Clean-up after tree removal" class="rounded-2xl shadow-xl" loading="lazy" />
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-normal">Moving Materials &amp; Clean-up</h2>
        <div class="section-divider mt-5"></div>
        <p class="mt-6 leading-relaxed">Often getting the tree on the ground is not half of the job and it is the clean-up where the work begins. We have the experience and tools to make light work of a big job and pride ourselves in leaving a work-site in a more tidy state than when we arrived.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="assessment" class="py-16 lg:py-24">
    <div class="site-container">
      <div class="grid items-center gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-16">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-normal">Tree Assessments</h2>
          <div class="section-divider mt-5"></div>
          <p class="mt-6 leading-relaxed">Professional assessment of trees by Certified Danger-Tree Assessor with decades of local experience.</p>
        </div>
        <img src="/images/20221006_093805.jpg" alt="Tree assessment" class="rounded-2xl shadow-xl" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-forest-dark py-16 text-white lg:py-20">
    <div class="site-container">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-normal text-white">Experience &amp; Certification</h2>
      <div class="mt-5 h-1 w-20 bg-forest-light"></div>
      <ul class="mt-8 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-forest-light">✓</span> BC Certified Faller for 25+ years</li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-forest-light">✓</span> Professional Arborist and Tree Climber of 22+ years</li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-forest-light">✓</span> Certified Wildlife/Danger-Tree Assessor for Parks and Rec.</li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-forest-light">✓</span> Level 3 First Aid</li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-forest-light">✓</span> Certified in Permaculture Landscape Design</li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-forest-light">✓</span> Fully-Insured — 5 Million Liability</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
